subsection.def:
appellant
                    (上訴人) means any party bringing any appeal
                before the Tribunal;

applicant
                    (申請人) means any party bringing any other
                proceedings before the Tribunal;

section.def:
Authority
                                (主管當局) has the same meaning as in
                                section 2 of the Ordinance;

Director
                (署長) has the same meaning as in the
            Ordinance;

Ordinance
                (條例) means the Roads (Works, Use and
            Compensation) Ordinance (Cap. 370);

Ordinance
                (條例) means the Electricity Networks (Statutory
            Easements) Ordinance (Cap. 357);
